Package util

Class LoginLogs

java.lang.Object
util.LoginLogs
Direct Known Subclasses:
AdminLoginLogs, EmployeeLoginLogs
public class LoginLogs extends Object
The LoginLogs class represents login logs of users. It contains information such as log ID, user ID, log type, and log time.
